2278953,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"quote":{"pid":"f155bf6ba369f428efd6d11b069c47fa66dbdd20","tid":2278953,"uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:16:03.000Z","msg":"點睇你個神種族滅絕古埃及人"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:18:19.000Z","msg":"其實耶穌信果個神, 未必同舊約果個神係同一個,"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:55:39.000Z","msg":"你傻咗？仲話信教二十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聖經就係聖經 經上所寫就係真理<br />\n你個普通人憑乜嘢自己定義經上所講<br />\n<br />\n舊約所講係罪與罰，新約就係基督嘅救恩<br />\n神只有一個，神遣佢嘅獨生子為人類贖罪而犧牲<br />\n免除我哋身上嘅罪，使我哋領受基督嘅救恩 <br />\n係基督重新歸來之前，我哋都係身處新約當中。<br />\n<br />\n唔知你乜教，我就天主教嘅。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過對上兩年我都係自己讀聖經<br />\n再同美國嘅新教牧師討論，學習<br />\n亦都同過東正教嘅牧師傾過計<br />\n舊約係過去，新約係當下<br />\n耶穌基督嘅犧牲就係同人類重新立約。<br />\n冇人會好似你咁講唔係同一個神<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/mask.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/mask.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/mask.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我仍然謹記舊約中上帝嘅公義<br />\n同埋猶太人嘅律法"},{"pid":"a9574489660a3c76c641bde844cfeda328e75e0e","tid":2278953,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f638bdae9a82da310eae59fd4b7aaf636fc6901e","tid":2278953,"uid":374184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2017871b641dfd1a8e7e69650a1f4a1194d056b","tid":2278953,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"55311b909f7a05538695ed28919852a5bc18d2f6","tid":2278953,"uid":347528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:38:18.000Z","msg":"由此看出你已經唔係基督徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/sm